Happy 72th independence day Indonesia!

30 July 2017

Thank you Allah for giving me another chance to put a smile upon the finish line of my 2nd Full Marathon. Immensely grateful to have persevere and strong running buddies, my mom and dad. I won't forget all the things I've been through before the finish line: from tiring long run practices, weight trainings, cheerful marshalls, free flow pocari sweat to mental breakdowns in last few kilometers. But I believe gritty efforts and prayers won't lie to the results (sub 6 hours Alhamdulillah). Can't wait for the next marathon.
